Human Capital 



People are our most valuable assets and the key to the long-term success of our clients and our firm.
We focus on hiring individuals with demonstrated intelligence, passion, dedication, teamwork, integrity and work ethic. We welcome the opportunity to speak with talented professionals who have relevant credentials and experience in investment management and advice, client service, corporate finance, legal & compliance, wealth management, administrative support or other relevant areas.


Seven Post is an equal employment opportunity employer.  We adhere to a policy of making employment decisions without regard to race, color, religion, gender, sexual orientation, national origin, ethnicity, age, genetic information, or disability.
You are accessing this employment-related information of your own volition and not as a result of any solicitation by a Seven Post employee.  Please select the following e-mail link to proceed and provide us with your name and relevant career information: human.capital@sevenpost.com
If we have further interest, we will contact you for a private and confidential discussion.  Thank you for your interest.










